modules.description: Generates first-class constructor values, pattern matching helpers, and folding/iterating capabilities for OCaml variant types. Works with variant type definitions to enable runtime inspection and traversal of constructors. Enables safe and efficient processing of all possible variants in a type-safe manner.

Provides functions to generate code for variant types, including pretty-printing and parsing. Works with OCaml's variant type representations and ppxlib's internal data structures. Used to automatically derive serialization and deserialization logic for custom variant types.
